{"tid":1518623,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"胡錫進代表支共直接干預一國兩制","createTime":"2019-08-30T09:56:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-30T12:27:38.000Z","uid":6435,"like":4,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"b4fcb1e9fc28e8c71c6062ea003a73d2e19f08c0","tid":1518623,"uid":6435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T09:56:21.000Z","msg":"派官員唔方便 就搵官媒總編出手<br />\n<br />\n胡錫進：法官迅速允許黃之鋒等人保釋　會傳遞不利信號<br />\n<br />\n香港眾志秘書長黃之鋒和成員周庭今早先後被捕，下午提堂後獲准保釋。內地《環球時報》總編輯胡錫進發微博表示，法官迅速允許黃之鋒等人保釋，他認為反映香港法律在應對暴亂方面存在軟弱的缺陷。法官迅速允許他們保釋，會向社會傳遞不利於止暴制亂的信號。法治目的就是要維繫社會的正常秩序，而現在香港秩序受到空前的挑戰，給煽動、組織和參與非法示威的人如此寬鬆的對待，不利於恢復受到侵蝕的法治的權威。胡錫進認為，在這個特殊時期，香港需要把止暴制亂的更多法律資源動員起來，應對那部分最極端的勢力向香港法治秩序發起的挑戰。<br />\n<br />\n2019-08-30 17:41:27<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/rthk_new_c/72283\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Frthk_new_c%2F72283&d=zmS1uFJnVw4lvQjuvPvUihV%2B9HGzyIzIqBo2vIhly3s%3D&h=fe462972\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/rthk_new_c/72283</a>"},{"pid":"cb2ba0dc842d4a2ce64560bc0db8575684ce8fb2","tid":1518623,"uid":123991,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T09:56:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OUQvG7y.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOUQvG7y.gif&h=0b84475f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n九月一號下午一點機場見<br />\n<br />\n901機場和你塞 Channel<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=zmS1uFJnVw4lvQjuvPvUihV%2B9HGzyIzIqBo2vIhly3s%3D&h=78712ce7\" target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/stuckwithyou</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 公海<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyouopen\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyouopen&d=zmS1uFJnVw4lvQjuvPvUihV%2B9HGzyIzIqBo2vIhly3s%3D&h=1171794b\" target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/stuckwithyouopen</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 宣傳<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyoupromote\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2F